{
  "version": "Notebook/1.0",
  "items": [
    {
      "type": 1,
      "content": {
        "json": "# Stale Device Investigation\n\nA guided workflow for identifying, triaging, and actioning Windows devices that have stopped checking in. Work through each step below to investigate and clean up your stale device fleet."
      },
      "name": "header"
    },
    {
      "type": 9,
      "content": {
        "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "id": "tab-param",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "Tab",
            "type": 1,
            "isRequired": true,
            "isHiddenWhenLocked": true,
            "value": "Scope"
          },
          {
            "id": "stale-days",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "StaleDays",
            "type": 1,
            "isRequired": true,
            "label": "Stale Threshold (days)",
            "value": "30"
          },
          {
            "id": "selected-device",
            "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
            "name": "SelectedDeviceId",
            "type": 1,
            "isHiddenWhenLocked": true,
            "value": ""
          }
        ],
        "style": "pills",
        "queryType": 0,
        "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
      },
      "name": "parameters"
    },
    {
      "type": 11,
      "content": {
        "version": "LinkItem/1.0",
        "style": "tabs",
        "links": [
          {
            "id": "scope-tab",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "1. Scope the Problem",
            "subTarget": "Scope",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "triage-tab",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "2. Triage",
            "subTarget": "Triage",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "investigate-tab",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "3. Investigate Devices",
            "subTarget": "Investigate",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "users-tab",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "4. Check Users",
            "subTarget": "Users",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "action-tab",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "5. Plan Cleanup",
            "subTarget": "Actions",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "deepdive-tab",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "6. Deep Dive",
            "subTarget": "DeepDive",
            "style": "link"
          },
          {
            "id": "trends-tab",
            "cellValue": "Tab",
            "linkTarget": "parameter",
            "linkLabel": "7. Trends",
            "subTarget": "Trends",
            "style": "link"
          }
        ]
      },
      "name": "tabs"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Step 1: Scope the Problem\n\nHow many Windows devices have gone stale? How bad is the situation? Start here to understand the scale before diving into individual devices."
            },
            "name": "scope-intro"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| summarize Total = count()",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Total Windows Devices",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "stat",
              "statSettings": {
                "valueColumn": "Total",
                "colorSettings": {
                  "mode": "default",
                  "palette": "blue"
                }
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "20",
            "name": "stat-total-windows"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| summarize Stale = count()",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Stale (>{StaleDays} days)",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "stat",
              "statSettings": {
                "valueColumn": "Stale",
                "colorSettings": {
                  "mode": "default",
                  "palette": "red"
                }
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "20",
            "name": "stat-total-stale"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| summarize Total = count(), Stale = countif(LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays}))\r\n| extend StalePercent = round(100.0 * Stale / Total, 1)\r\n| project StalePercent",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Stale Rate %",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "stat",
              "statSettings": {
                "valueColumn": "StalePercent",
                "postfix": "%",
                "colorSettings": {
                  "mode": "default",
                  "palette": "orange"
                }
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "20",
            "name": "stat-stale-rate"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > 180\r\n| summarize Critical = count()",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Critical (6+ months)",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "stat",
              "statSettings": {
                "valueColumn": "Critical",
                "colorSettings": {
                  "mode": "default",
                  "palette": "redBright"
                }
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "20",
            "name": "stat-critical"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| where IsEncrypted != \"true\"\r\n| summarize Unencrypted = count()",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Stale + Unencrypted",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "stat",
              "statSettings": {
                "valueColumn": "Unencrypted",
                "colorSettings": {
                  "mode": "default",
                  "palette": "redBright"
                }
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "20",
            "name": "stat-unencrypted"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "---\n### How long have these devices been stale?"
            },
            "name": "scope-section-duration"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| extend StaleSeverity = case(\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, \"Critical - 6+ months\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 90,  \"High - 3-6 months\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 60,  \"Medium - 2-3 months\",\r\n    \"Low - 1-2 months\")\r\n| summarize Devices = count() by StaleSeverity\r\n| order by case(\r\n    StaleSeverity startswith \"Critical\", 1,\r\n    StaleSeverity startswith \"High\", 2,\r\n    StaleSeverity startswith \"Medium\", 3,\r\n    4) asc",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "Severity Breakdown",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "piechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Critical - 6+ months",
                    "color": "redBright"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "High - 3-6 months",
                    "color": "orange"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Medium - 2-3 months",
                    "color": "yellow"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Low - 1-2 months",
                    "color": "blue"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "40",
            "name": "chart-severity-pie"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| extend AgeBucket = case(\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 365, \"12+ months\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 270, \"9-12 months\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, \"6-9 months\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 90,  \"3-6 months\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 60,  \"2-3 months\",\r\n    \"1-2 months\")\r\n| summarize Devices = count() by AgeBucket\r\n| order by case(\r\n    AgeBucket == \"12+ months\", 6,\r\n    AgeBucket == \"9-12 months\", 5,\r\n    AgeBucket == \"6-9 months\", 4,\r\n    AgeBucket == \"3-6 months\", 3,\r\n    AgeBucket == \"2-3 months\", 2,\r\n    1) asc",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "Stale Duration Distribution",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "xAxis": "AgeBucket",
                "yAxis": [
                  "Devices"
                ],
                "showDataLabels": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "60",
            "name": "chart-age-distribution"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "---\n### Which hardware models are affected most?\n*If a particular model dominates, it may indicate a hardware recall, end-of-life, or deployment issue.*"
            },
            "name": "scope-section-models"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| summarize Devices = count(), AvgDaysStale = round(avg(LastSyncDaysAgo), 0) by Model, Manufacturer\r\n| order by Devices desc\r\n| take 15",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Top 15 Stale Models",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Devices",
                    "formatter": 4,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AvgDaysStale",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "min": 30,
                      "max": 365
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "Devices",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "grid-top-models"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "\n> **Next step:** Now that you know the scale, move to **Step 2: Triage** to see what the system recommends for each device."
            },
            "name": "scope-next"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "Scope"
      },
      "name": "scope-group"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Step 2: Triage\n\nDevices are automatically classified by risk level based on staleness duration, user account status, and ownership signals. Use this summary to understand the recommended actions before diving into individual devices."
            },
            "name": "triage-intro"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let StaleDevicesList = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays});\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nlet UsersByIdLookup = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId;\r\nStaleDevicesList\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, AccountEnabled\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByIdLookup | project LastLoggedOnUserId = UserId, LastLogonAccountEnabled = AccountEnabled\r\n) on LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| extend BestKnownAccountEnabled = coalesce(LastLogonAccountEnabled, AccountEnabled)\r\n| extend RecommendedAction = case(\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire - user disabled, device abandoned\",\r\n    isempty(UserPrincipalName) and isempty(LastLoggedOnUserId) and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire - no user, long stale\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, \"Retire - 6+ months uncontacted\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Investigate - likely lost or decommissioned\",\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Investigate - user disabled, device recent\",\r\n    \"Monitor - recently went stale\")\r\n| extend ActionCategory = case(\r\n    RecommendedAction startswith \"Retire\", \"Retire\",\r\n    RecommendedAction startswith \"Investigate\", \"Investigate\",\r\n    \"Monitor\")\r\n| summarize Devices = count() by ActionCategory\r\n| order by case(ActionCategory == \"Retire\", 1, ActionCategory == \"Investigate\", 2, 3) asc",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "Action Breakdown",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "piechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Retire",
                    "color": "redBright"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Investigate",
                    "color": "orange"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Monitor",
                    "color": "blue"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "40",
            "name": "chart-action-pie"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let StaleDevicesList = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays});\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nlet UsersByIdLookup = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId;\r\nStaleDevicesList\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, AccountEnabled\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByIdLookup | project LastLoggedOnUserId = UserId, LastLogonAccountEnabled = AccountEnabled\r\n) on LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| extend BestKnownAccountEnabled = coalesce(LastLogonAccountEnabled, AccountEnabled)\r\n| extend RecommendedAction = case(\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire - user disabled, device abandoned\",\r\n    isempty(UserPrincipalName) and isempty(LastLoggedOnUserId) and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire - no user, long stale\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, \"Retire - 6+ months uncontacted\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Investigate - likely lost or decommissioned\",\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Investigate - user disabled, device recent\",\r\n    \"Monitor - recently went stale\")\r\n| summarize\r\n    Devices = count(),\r\n    AvgDaysStale = round(avg(LastSyncDaysAgo), 0),\r\n    MaxDaysStale = max(LastSyncDaysAgo),\r\n    OrphanedCount = countif(BestKnownAccountEnabled == false),\r\n    UnencryptedCount = countif(IsEncrypted != \"true\")\r\n    by RecommendedAction\r\n| order by case(\r\n    RecommendedAction startswith \"Retire\", 1,\r\n    RecommendedAction startswith \"Investigate\", 2,\r\n    3) asc, Devices desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Action Detail",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "RecommendedAction",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Retire",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Investigate",
                          "representation": "warning",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "pending",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Devices",
                    "formatter": 4,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AvgDaysStale",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "min": 30,
                      "max": 365
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "MaxDaysStale",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "min": 30,
                      "max": 365
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "OrphanedCount",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": ">",
                          "thresholdValue": "0",
                          "representation": "warning",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "0"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "UnencryptedCount",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": ">",
                          "thresholdValue": "0",
                          "representation": "warning",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "0"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "60",
            "name": "grid-action-summary"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "\n> **Next step:** Go to **Step 3: Investigate Devices** for the full device list with search, model/department filters, and click-through to the **Deep Dive** tab."
            },
            "name": "triage-next"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "Triage"
      },
      "name": "triage-group"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Step 3: Investigate Devices\n\nDig into individual devices. This is the full detail view with every field available for investigation. Use the search box and column filters to find specific devices. Export to Excel for offline work."
            },
            "name": "investigate-intro"
          },
          {
            "type": 9,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
              "parameters": [
                {
                  "id": "device-search",
                  "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
                  "name": "DeviceSearch",
                  "type": 1,
                  "label": "Search (device name, serial, user)",
                  "value": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": "model-filter",
                  "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
                  "name": "ModelFilter",
                  "type": 2,
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "multiSelect": true,
                  "quote": "'",
                  "delimiter": ",",
                  "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| extend ModelName = coalesce(Model, \"Unknown\")\r\n| distinct ModelName\r\n| order by ModelName asc",
                  "typeSettings": {
                    "additionalResourceOptions": [
                      "value::all"
                    ],
                    "showDefault": false
                  },
                  "defaultValue": "value::all",
                  "queryType": 0,
                  "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
                  "label": "Model",
                  "value": [
                    "value::all"
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "id": "dept-filter",
                  "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
                  "name": "DeptFilter",
                  "type": 2,
                  "isRequired": true,
                  "multiSelect": true,
                  "quote": "'",
                  "delimiter": ",",
                  "query": "let StaleDevicesList = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays});\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nStaleDevicesList\r\n| join kind=leftouter (UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, Department) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| extend Dept = coalesce(Department, \"No Data\")\r\n| distinct Dept\r\n| order by Dept asc",
                  "typeSettings": {
                    "additionalResourceOptions": [
                      "value::all"
                    ],
                    "showDefault": false
                  },
                  "defaultValue": "value::all",
                  "queryType": 0,
                  "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
                  "label": "Department",
                  "value": [
                    "value::all"
                  ]
                }
              ],
              "style": "pills",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
            },
            "name": "investigate-filters"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let StaleDays = toint({StaleDays});\r\nlet StaleDevicesList = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > StaleDays;\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nlet UsersByIdLookup = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId;\r\nStaleDevicesList\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByUPN\r\n    | project UserPrincipalName, PrimaryUserId = UserId, Department, JobTitle, OfficeLocation, City, Country, AccountEnabled, LastSignInDateTime\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByIdLookup\r\n    | project LastLoggedOnUserId = UserId, LastLogonUserUPN = UserPrincipalName, LastLogonUserName = DisplayName, LastLogonUserDept = Department, LastLogonAccountEnabled = AccountEnabled\r\n) on LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| extend\r\n    LastLogonDaysAgo = iff(isnotempty(LastLoggedOnDateTime), datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastLoggedOnDateTime)), int(null)),\r\n    LastSignInDaysAgo = iff(isnotempty(LastSignInDateTime), datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSignInDateTime)), int(null)),\r\n    EnrolledDaysAgo = iff(isnotempty(EnrolledDateTime), datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(EnrolledDateTime)), int(null))\r\n| extend\r\n    BestKnownUserId = coalesce(LastLoggedOnUserId, PrimaryUserId, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownUser = coalesce(LastLogonUserUPN, UserPrincipalName, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownName = coalesce(LastLogonUserName, UserDisplayName, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownDept = coalesce(LastLogonUserDept, Department, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled = coalesce(LastLogonAccountEnabled, AccountEnabled)\r\n| extend StaleSeverity = case(\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, \"Critical - 6+ months\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 90,  \"High - 3-6 months\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 60,  \"Medium - 2-3 months\",\r\n    \"Low - 1-2 months\")\r\n| extend RecommendedAction = case(\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire - user disabled, device abandoned\",\r\n    isempty(UserPrincipalName) and isempty(LastLoggedOnUserId) and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire - no user, long stale\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, \"Retire - 6+ months uncontacted\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Investigate - likely lost or decommissioned\",\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Investigate - user disabled, device recent\",\r\n    \"Monitor - recently went stale\")\r\n| extend IsOrphaned = iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Yes\", iff(isnull(BestKnownAccountEnabled), \"Unknown\", \"No\"))\r\n| extend IsEncryptedLabel = case(IsEncrypted == \"true\", \"Yes\", IsEncrypted == \"false\", \"No\", \"Unknown\")\r\n| where '*' in ({ModelFilter}) or coalesce(Model, \"Unknown\") in ({ModelFilter})\r\n| where '*' in ({DeptFilter}) or BestKnownDept in ({DeptFilter})\r\n| where '{DeviceSearch}' == '' or DeviceName contains '{DeviceSearch}' or SerialNumber contains '{DeviceSearch}' or BestKnownUser contains '{DeviceSearch}' or BestKnownName contains '{DeviceSearch}'\r\n| project\r\n    StaleSeverity, RecommendedAction, IsOrphaned,\r\n    DeviceName, SerialNumber,\r\n    BestKnownUser, BestKnownName, BestKnownDept,\r\n    AccountActive = iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == true, \"Active\", iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Disabled\", \"Unknown\")),\r\n    LastSyncDateTime, LastSyncDaysAgo,\r\n    LastLoggedOnDateTime, LastLogonDaysAgo,\r\n    Model, Manufacturer, IsEncryptedLabel,\r\n    OwnerType = iff(isnotempty(OwnerType), OwnerType, \"No Data\"),\r\n    JoinType = iff(isnotempty(JoinType), JoinType, \"No Data\"),\r\n    ChassisType = iff(isnotempty(ChassisType) and ChassisType != \"unknown\", ChassisType, \"No Data\"),\r\n    ComplianceState, ManagementState,\r\n    OSVersion,\r\n    EnrolledDateTime, EnrolledDaysAgo,\r\n    DeviceId,\r\n    LastLoggedOnUserId = iff(isnotempty(LastLoggedOnUserId), LastLoggedOnUserId, \"No Data\"),\r\n    UsersLoggedOnJson = iff(isnotempty(UsersLoggedOnJson), UsersLoggedOnJson, \"No Data\")\r\n| order by LastSyncDaysAgo desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Full Device Details",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "StaleSeverity",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "Sev0",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "High",
                          "representation": "Sev1",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Medium",
                          "representation": "Sev2",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "Sev3",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "RecommendedAction",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Retire",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Investigate",
                          "representation": "warning",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "pending",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "IsOrphaned",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Yes",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "Yes"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "No",
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "No"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "unknown",
                          "text": "Unknown"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AccountActive",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Active",
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "Active"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Disabled",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "Disabled"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "unknown",
                          "text": "Unknown"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "LastSyncDaysAgo",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "min": 30,
                      "max": 365
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "IsEncryptedLabel",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Yes",
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "Yes"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "No",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "No"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "unknown",
                          "text": "Unknown"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "DeviceId",
                    "formatter": 5
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "UsersLoggedOnJson",
                    "formatter": 5
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "LastSyncDaysAgo",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ],
                "labelSettings": [
                  {
                    "columnId": "DeviceName",
                    "label": "Device Name"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "grid-full-details"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "\n> **Tip:** Copy a device name from the grid above, then go to **Step 6: Deep Dive** and search for it to see a full investigation with compliance details, user profile, and contact information.\n\n> **Next step:** Need to chase down device owners? Go to **Step 4: Check Users** to see which users have the most stale devices and whether their accounts are still active."
            },
            "name": "investigate-next"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "Investigate"
      },
      "name": "investigate-group"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Step 4: Check Users\n\nWho are the users behind these stale devices? Are their accounts still active? If a user's account is disabled, their devices are almost certainly safe to retire. If active, you'll need to contact them."
            },
            "name": "users-intro"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let StaleDevicesList = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays});\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nlet UsersByIdLookup = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId;\r\nStaleDevicesList\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, AccountEnabled\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByIdLookup | project LastLoggedOnUserId = UserId, LastLogonAccountEnabled = AccountEnabled\r\n) on LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| extend BestKnownAccountEnabled = coalesce(LastLogonAccountEnabled, AccountEnabled)\r\n| summarize\r\n    Total = count(),\r\n    UserActive = countif(BestKnownAccountEnabled == true),\r\n    UserDisabled = countif(BestKnownAccountEnabled == false),\r\n    UserUnknown = countif(isnull(BestKnownAccountEnabled))\r\n| project\r\n    label = \"User Account Status\",\r\n    Active = UserActive,\r\n    Disabled = UserDisabled,\r\n    Unknown = UserUnknown",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Stale Devices by User Account Status",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "tiles",
              "tileSettings": {
                "titleContent": {
                  "columnMatch": "label",
                  "formatter": 1
                },
                "showBorder": false
              }
            },
            "name": "tiles-user-status"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let StaleDevicesList = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays});\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nlet UsersByIdLookup = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId;\r\nStaleDevicesList\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, AccountEnabled\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByIdLookup | project LastLoggedOnUserId = UserId, LastLogonAccountEnabled = AccountEnabled\r\n) on LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| extend BestKnownAccountEnabled = coalesce(LastLogonAccountEnabled, AccountEnabled)\r\n| extend AccountStatus = iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == true, \"Active\", iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Disabled\", \"Unknown\"))\r\n| summarize Devices = count() by AccountStatus",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "Devices by User Account Status",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "piechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Active",
                    "color": "green"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Disabled",
                    "color": "redBright"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Unknown",
                    "color": "gray"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "40",
            "name": "chart-user-status-pie"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let StaleDevicesList = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays});\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nStaleDevicesList\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, Department\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| extend Dept = coalesce(Department, \"No Data\")\r\n| summarize\r\n    TotalStale = count(),\r\n    AvgDaysStale = round(avg(LastSyncDaysAgo), 0),\r\n    Critical = countif(LastSyncDaysAgo > 180),\r\n    High = countif(LastSyncDaysAgo > 90 and LastSyncDaysAgo <= 180)\r\n    by Dept\r\n| order by TotalStale desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Stale Devices by Department - Who to Contact",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "TotalStale",
                    "formatter": 4,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AvgDaysStale",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "min": 30,
                      "max": 365
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Critical",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": ">",
                          "thresholdValue": "0",
                          "representation": "Sev0",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "0"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "High",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": ">",
                          "thresholdValue": "0",
                          "representation": "Sev1",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "0"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "TotalStale",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "60",
            "name": "grid-department-summary"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "---\n### Users with Multiple Stale Devices\n*These users may have left the organisation, changed roles, or been issued replacements without returning old hardware.*"
            },
            "name": "users-section-multi"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let StaleDevicesList = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays});\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nlet UsersByIdLookup = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId;\r\nStaleDevicesList\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, PrimaryUserId = UserId, Department, JobTitle, AccountEnabled, LastSignInDateTime\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByIdLookup | project LastLoggedOnUserId = UserId, LastLogonUserUPN = UserPrincipalName, LastLogonUserName = DisplayName, LastLogonAccountEnabled = AccountEnabled\r\n) on LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| extend\r\n    BestKnownUser = coalesce(LastLogonUserUPN, UserPrincipalName, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownName = coalesce(LastLogonUserName, UserDisplayName, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownDept = coalesce(Department, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled = coalesce(LastLogonAccountEnabled, AccountEnabled)\r\n| where BestKnownUser != \"No Data\"\r\n| summarize\r\n    StaleDeviceCount = count(),\r\n    Devices = make_list(DeviceName, 10),\r\n    WorstDaysStale = max(LastSyncDaysAgo)\r\n    by BestKnownUser, BestKnownName, BestKnownDept, AccountActive = iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == true, \"Active\", iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Disabled\", \"Unknown\")), JobTitle = iff(isnotempty(JobTitle), JobTitle, \"No Data\")\r\n| where StaleDeviceCount > 1\r\n| extend DeviceList = strcat_array(Devices, \", \")\r\n| project BestKnownUser, BestKnownName, AccountActive, BestKnownDept, JobTitle, StaleDeviceCount, WorstDaysStale, DeviceList\r\n| order by StaleDeviceCount desc, WorstDaysStale desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Users with 2+ Stale Devices",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AccountActive",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Active",
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "Active"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Disabled",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "Disabled"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "unknown",
                          "text": "Unknown"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "StaleDeviceCount",
                    "formatter": 4,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "WorstDaysStale",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "min": 30,
                      "max": 365
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "StaleDeviceCount",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "grid-multi-device-users"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "---\n### Devices with No Known User\n*These devices have no assigned UPN and no last logon user ID. They may be shared devices, kiosks, or devices that were enrolled but never used.*"
            },
            "name": "users-section-nouser"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| where isempty(UserPrincipalName) and isempty(LastLoggedOnUserId)\r\n| project\r\n    DeviceName, SerialNumber,\r\n    Model, Manufacturer,\r\n    LastSyncDateTime, LastSyncDaysAgo,\r\n    EnrolledDateTime,\r\n    ComplianceState, ManagementState,\r\n    JoinType = iff(isnotempty(JoinType), JoinType, \"No Data\"),\r\n    IsEncrypted = case(IsEncrypted == \"true\", \"Yes\", IsEncrypted == \"false\", \"No\", \"Unknown\")\r\n| order by LastSyncDaysAgo desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Orphaned Devices (No User)",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "LastSyncDaysAgo",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "min": 30,
                      "max": 365
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "IsEncrypted",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Yes",
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "Yes"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "No",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "No"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "unknown",
                          "text": "Unknown"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "LastSyncDaysAgo",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "grid-no-user-devices"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "\n> **Next step:** Ready to act? Go to **Step 5: Plan Cleanup** for a summary you can hand off to your team or use to batch-retire devices."
            },
            "name": "users-next"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "Users"
      },
      "name": "users-group"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Step 5: Plan Cleanup\n\nYou've scoped the problem, triaged by severity, investigated individual devices, and checked user accounts. Now plan the cleanup. Export these lists and work through them with your team."
            },
            "name": "actions-intro"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "### Ready to Retire\n*These devices are recommended for immediate retirement: user account disabled with 90+ days stale, no known user with 90+ days stale, or 6+ months uncontacted. Export this list and process in Intune.*"
            },
            "name": "actions-section-retire"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let StaleDevicesList = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays});\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nlet UsersByIdLookup = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId;\r\nStaleDevicesList\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, AccountEnabled\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByIdLookup | project LastLoggedOnUserId = UserId, LastLogonUserUPN = UserPrincipalName, LastLogonAccountEnabled = AccountEnabled\r\n) on LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| extend\r\n    BestKnownUser = coalesce(LastLogonUserUPN, UserPrincipalName, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled = coalesce(LastLogonAccountEnabled, AccountEnabled)\r\n| extend RecommendedAction = case(\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire - user disabled, device abandoned\",\r\n    isempty(UserPrincipalName) and isempty(LastLoggedOnUserId) and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire - no user, long stale\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, \"Retire - 6+ months uncontacted\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Investigate\",\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Investigate\",\r\n    \"Monitor\")\r\n| where RecommendedAction startswith \"Retire\"\r\n| project\r\n    RecommendedAction,\r\n    DeviceName, SerialNumber, DeviceId,\r\n    BestKnownUser,\r\n    LastSyncDateTime, LastSyncDaysAgo,\r\n    Model, Manufacturer,\r\n    IsEncrypted = case(IsEncrypted == \"true\", \"Yes\", IsEncrypted == \"false\", \"No\", \"Unknown\")\r\n| order by LastSyncDaysAgo desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Devices to Retire",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "RecommendedAction",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "LastSyncDaysAgo",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "min": 30,
                      "max": 365
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "DeviceId",
                    "formatter": 5
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "IsEncrypted",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Yes",
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "Yes"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "No",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "No"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "unknown",
                          "text": "Unknown"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "LastSyncDaysAgo",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "grid-retire-list"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "---\n### Needs Investigation\n*These devices need manual investigation before a decision can be made. Contact the user or check with their manager.*"
            },
            "name": "actions-section-investigate"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let StaleDevicesList = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays});\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nlet UsersByIdLookup = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId;\r\nStaleDevicesList\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, Department, AccountEnabled\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByIdLookup | project LastLoggedOnUserId = UserId, LastLogonUserUPN = UserPrincipalName, LastLogonUserName = DisplayName, LastLogonAccountEnabled = AccountEnabled\r\n) on LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| extend\r\n    BestKnownUser = coalesce(LastLogonUserUPN, UserPrincipalName, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownName = coalesce(LastLogonUserName, UserDisplayName, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownDept = coalesce(Department, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled = coalesce(LastLogonAccountEnabled, AccountEnabled)\r\n| extend RecommendedAction = case(\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire\",\r\n    isempty(UserPrincipalName) and isempty(LastLoggedOnUserId) and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, \"Retire\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Investigate - likely lost or decommissioned\",\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Investigate - user disabled, device recent\",\r\n    \"Monitor\")\r\n| where RecommendedAction startswith \"Investigate\"\r\n| project\r\n    RecommendedAction,\r\n    DeviceName, SerialNumber,\r\n    BestKnownUser, BestKnownName, BestKnownDept,\r\n    AccountActive = iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == true, \"Active\", iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Disabled\", \"Unknown\")),\r\n    LastSyncDateTime, LastSyncDaysAgo,\r\n    Model\r\n| order by LastSyncDaysAgo desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Devices to Investigate",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "RecommendedAction",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "warning",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AccountActive",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Active",
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "Active"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Disabled",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "Disabled"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "unknown",
                          "text": "Unknown"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "LastSyncDaysAgo",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "min": 30,
                      "max": 365
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "LastSyncDaysAgo",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "grid-investigate-list"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "---\n### Monitor\n*Recently stale devices that may come back online. Check again next cycle.*"
            },
            "name": "actions-section-monitor"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let StaleDevicesList = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays});\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nlet UsersByIdLookup = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId;\r\nStaleDevicesList\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, Department, AccountEnabled\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByIdLookup | project LastLoggedOnUserId = UserId, LastLogonUserUPN = UserPrincipalName, LastLogonAccountEnabled = AccountEnabled\r\n) on LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| extend\r\n    BestKnownUser = coalesce(LastLogonUserUPN, UserPrincipalName, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownDept = coalesce(Department, \"No Data\"),\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled = coalesce(LastLogonAccountEnabled, AccountEnabled)\r\n| extend RecommendedAction = case(\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire\",\r\n    isempty(UserPrincipalName) and isempty(LastLoggedOnUserId) and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, \"Retire\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Investigate\",\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Investigate\",\r\n    \"Monitor - recently went stale\")\r\n| where RecommendedAction startswith \"Monitor\"\r\n| project\r\n    DeviceName, SerialNumber,\r\n    BestKnownUser, BestKnownDept,\r\n    LastSyncDateTime, LastSyncDaysAgo,\r\n    Model\r\n| order by LastSyncDaysAgo desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Devices to Monitor",
              "showExportToExcel": true,
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "LastSyncDaysAgo",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "min": 30,
                      "max": 365
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true,
                "sortBy": [
                  {
                    "itemKey": "LastSyncDaysAgo",
                    "sortOrder": 2
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "name": "grid-monitor-list"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "Actions"
      },
      "name": "actions-group"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Step 6: Deep Dive\n\nFull investigation panel for a single device. The dropdown below shows devices matching your filters from **Step 3: Investigate Devices**."
            },
            "name": "deepdive-intro"
          },
          {
            "type": 9,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
              "parameters": [
                {
                  "id": "device-search-dd",
                  "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
                  "name": "DeviceSearchDD",
                  "type": 1,
                  "label": "Search device name or serial",
                  "value": ""
                },
                {
                  "id": "device-selector",
                  "version": "KqlParameterItem/1.0",
                  "name": "SelectedDeviceId",
                  "type": 2,
                  "isRequired": false,
                  "query": "let UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nlet UsersByIdLookup = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId;\r\nIntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| join kind=leftouter (UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, Department) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (UsersByIdLookup | project LastLoggedOnUserId = UserId, LastLogonUserDept = Department) on LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| extend BestKnownDept = coalesce(LastLogonUserDept, Department, \"No Data\")\r\n| where '*' in ({ModelFilter}) or coalesce(Model, \"Unknown\") in ({ModelFilter})\r\n| where '*' in ({DeptFilter}) or BestKnownDept in ({DeptFilter})\r\n| where '{DeviceSearchDD}' == '' or DeviceName contains '{DeviceSearchDD}' or SerialNumber contains '{DeviceSearchDD}'\r\n| project label = strcat(DeviceName, ' (', coalesce(SerialNumber, 'no serial'), ') - ', LastSyncDaysAgo, 'd stale'), value = DeviceId\r\n| order by label asc",
                  "typeSettings": {
                    "showDefault": false
                  },
                  "queryType": 0,
                  "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
                  "label": "Select Device"
                }
              ],
              "style": "pills",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces"
            },
            "name": "deepdive-params"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "### Select a device to investigate\n\nUse the search box to filter the dropdown, or set filters in **Step 3: Investigate Devices** — they carry over here."
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "name": "deepdive-no-device"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where DeviceId == '{SelectedDeviceId}'\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| project DaysSinceSync = LastSyncDaysAgo",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Days Since Last Sync",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "stat",
              "statSettings": {
                "valueColumn": "DaysSinceSync",
                "colorSettings": {
                  "mode": "thresholds",
                  "thresholds": [
                    {
                      "isDefault": true,
                      "color": "blue",
                      "text": "{0}"
                    },
                    {
                      "operator": ">",
                      "value": 60,
                      "color": "yellow",
                      "text": "{0}"
                    },
                    {
                      "operator": ">",
                      "value": 90,
                      "color": "orange",
                      "text": "{0}"
                    },
                    {
                      "operator": ">",
                      "value": 180,
                      "color": "redBright",
                      "text": "{0}"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "customWidth": "20",
            "name": "stat-days-stale"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where DeviceId == '{SelectedDeviceId}'\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| extend Severity = case(\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, \"Critical\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 90,  \"High\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 60,  \"Medium\",\r\n    \"Low\")\r\n| project Severity",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Severity",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "stat",
              "statSettings": {
                "valueColumn": "Severity",
                "colorSettings": {
                  "mode": "thresholds",
                  "thresholds": [
                    {
                      "isDefault": true,
                      "color": "blue",
                      "text": "{0}"
                    },
                    {
                      "operator": "==",
                      "value": "Critical",
                      "color": "redBright",
                      "text": "Critical"
                    },
                    {
                      "operator": "==",
                      "value": "High",
                      "color": "orange",
                      "text": "High"
                    },
                    {
                      "operator": "==",
                      "value": "Medium",
                      "color": "yellow",
                      "text": "Medium"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "customWidth": "20",
            "name": "stat-severity"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where DeviceId == '{SelectedDeviceId}'\r\n| project ComplianceState = coalesce(ComplianceState, \"Unknown\")",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Compliance",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "stat",
              "statSettings": {
                "valueColumn": "ComplianceState",
                "colorSettings": {
                  "mode": "thresholds",
                  "thresholds": [
                    {
                      "isDefault": true,
                      "color": "gray",
                      "text": "{0}"
                    },
                    {
                      "operator": "==",
                      "value": "compliant",
                      "color": "green",
                      "text": "Compliant"
                    },
                    {
                      "operator": "==",
                      "value": "noncompliant",
                      "color": "redBright",
                      "text": "Non-Compliant"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "customWidth": "20",
            "name": "stat-compliance"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where DeviceId == '{SelectedDeviceId}'\r\n| project Encrypted = case(IsEncrypted == \"true\", \"Yes\", IsEncrypted == \"false\", \"No\", \"Unknown\")",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "Encrypted",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "stat",
              "statSettings": {
                "valueColumn": "Encrypted",
                "colorSettings": {
                  "mode": "thresholds",
                  "thresholds": [
                    {
                      "isDefault": true,
                      "color": "gray",
                      "text": "{0}"
                    },
                    {
                      "operator": "==",
                      "value": "Yes",
                      "color": "green",
                      "text": "Yes"
                    },
                    {
                      "operator": "==",
                      "value": "No",
                      "color": "redBright",
                      "text": "No"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "customWidth": "20",
            "name": "stat-encrypted"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let Device = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where DeviceId == '{SelectedDeviceId}';\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nlet UsersByIdLookup = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId;\r\nDevice\r\n| join kind=leftouter (UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, AccountEnabled) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (UsersByIdLookup | project LastLoggedOnUserId = UserId, LastLogonAccountEnabled = AccountEnabled) on LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| extend BestKnownAccountEnabled = coalesce(LastLogonAccountEnabled, AccountEnabled)\r\n| project AccountStatus = iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == true, \"Active\", iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Disabled\", \"Unknown\"))",
              "size": 4,
              "title": "User Account",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "stat",
              "statSettings": {
                "valueColumn": "AccountStatus",
                "colorSettings": {
                  "mode": "thresholds",
                  "thresholds": [
                    {
                      "isDefault": true,
                      "color": "gray",
                      "text": "{0}"
                    },
                    {
                      "operator": "==",
                      "value": "Active",
                      "color": "green",
                      "text": "Active"
                    },
                    {
                      "operator": "==",
                      "value": "Disabled",
                      "color": "redBright",
                      "text": "Disabled"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "customWidth": "20",
            "name": "stat-user-account"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "---\n### Device Identity & Hardware"
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "name": "deepdive-section-identity"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where DeviceId == '{SelectedDeviceId}'\r\n| project\r\n    DeviceName, SerialNumber, AzureADDeviceId,\r\n    Manufacturer, Model,\r\n    ChassisType = iff(isnotempty(ChassisType) and ChassisType != \"unknown\", ChassisType, \"Unknown\"),\r\n    OperatingSystem, OSVersion,\r\n    TotalStorageGB, FreeStorageGB, PhysicalMemoryGB,\r\n    OwnerType = coalesce(OwnerType, \"Unknown\"),\r\n    JoinType = coalesce(JoinType, \"Unknown\"),\r\n    ManagementState, AutopilotEnrolled,\r\n    EnrolledDateTime",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Device Identity",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table"
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "customWidth": "60",
            "name": "deepdive-device-identity"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where DeviceId == '{SelectedDeviceId}'\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    IntuneUsers_CL\r\n    | summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName\r\n    | project UserPrincipalName, UserLastSignIn = LastSignInDateTime, UserLastNonInteractive = LastNonInteractiveSignInDateTime\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| extend\r\n    SyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime)),\r\n    LogonDaysAgo = iff(isnotempty(LastLoggedOnDateTime), datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastLoggedOnDateTime)), int(null)),\r\n    SignInDaysAgo = iff(isnotempty(UserLastSignIn), datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(UserLastSignIn)), int(null))\r\n| project p = pack_array(\r\n    pack(\"Signal\", \"Intune Sync\", \"DaysAgo\", SyncDaysAgo),\r\n    pack(\"Signal\", \"Device Logon\", \"DaysAgo\", LogonDaysAgo),\r\n    pack(\"Signal\", \"User Sign-In\", \"DaysAgo\", SignInDaysAgo))\r\n| mv-expand p\r\n| evaluate bag_unpack(p)\r\n| where isnotnull(DaysAgo) and tolong(DaysAgo) >= 0\r\n| extend DaysAgo = tolong(DaysAgo)\r\n| order by DaysAgo desc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Staleness Signals (days ago)",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "xAxis": "Signal",
                "yAxis": [
                  "DaysAgo"
                ],
                "showDataLabels": true,
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "DaysAgo",
                    "color": "orange"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "customWidth": "40",
            "name": "deepdive-staleness-barchart"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "---\n### User Profile\n*Primary assigned user and last logon user from Entra ID.*"
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "name": "deepdive-section-user"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let Device = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where DeviceId == '{SelectedDeviceId}'\r\n| project UserPrincipalName, UserDisplayName, LastLoggedOnUserId;\r\nlet PrimaryUser = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=inner (Device | where isnotempty(UserPrincipalName) | project UserPrincipalName) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| project Source = \"Primary\", UserPrincipalName, DisplayName, Mail, JobTitle, Department, OfficeLocation, AccountEnabled,\r\n    LastSignInDateTime, LastSignInDaysAgo = iff(isnotempty(LastSignInDateTime), datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSignInDateTime)), int(null));\r\nlet LastLogonUser = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId\r\n| join kind=inner (Device | where isnotempty(LastLoggedOnUserId) | project LastLoggedOnUserId) on $left.UserId == $right.LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| project Source = \"Last Logon\", UserPrincipalName, DisplayName, Mail, JobTitle, Department, OfficeLocation, AccountEnabled,\r\n    LastSignInDateTime, LastSignInDaysAgo = iff(isnotempty(LastSignInDateTime), datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSignInDateTime)), int(null));\r\nunion PrimaryUser, LastLogonUser\r\n| distinct *",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "User Profile (from Entra ID)",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AccountEnabled",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "true",
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "Active"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "True",
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "Active"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "false",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "Disabled"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "False",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "Disabled"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "unknown",
                          "text": "Unknown"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "LastSignInDaysAgo",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "min": 0,
                      "max": 180
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "name": "deepdive-user-profile"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "---\n### Contact & Location\n*Information to help locate the device and contact its assigned user.*"
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "name": "deepdive-section-contact"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nIntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where DeviceId == \"{SelectedDeviceId}\"\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByUPN\r\n    | project UserPrincipalName, UserMail = Mail, DisplayName, JobTitle, Department\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| project\r\n    [\"Email (Device)\"] = coalesce(EmailAddress, \"—\"),\r\n    [\"Email (Entra)\"] = coalesce(UserMail, \"Not available\"),\r\n    [\"Display Name\"] = coalesce(DisplayName, \"Not available\"),\r\n    [\"Job Title\"] = coalesce(JobTitle, \"Not available\"),\r\n    Department = coalesce(Department, \"Not available\")",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Contact Information",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "labelSettings": [
                  {
                    "columnId": "Email (Device)",
                    "label": "Email (Device)"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "Email (Entra)",
                    "label": "Email (Entra)"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "Display Name",
                    "label": "Display Name"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "Job Title",
                    "label": "Job Title"
                  },
                  {
                    "columnId": "Department",
                    "label": "Department"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "deepdive-contact-info"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nIntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where DeviceId == \"{SelectedDeviceId}\"\r\n| join kind=leftouter (\r\n    UsersByUPN\r\n    | project UserPrincipalName, OfficeLocation, City, State, Country\r\n) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| extend FormFactor = case(\r\n    ChassisType in (\"laptop\", \"notebook\"), \"Laptop\",\r\n    ChassisType in (\"desktop\", \"miniTower\", \"tower\"), \"Desktop\",\r\n    ChassisType in (\"tablet\"), \"Tablet\",\r\n    ChassisType == \"unknown\" or isempty(ChassisType), \"Unknown\",\r\n    ChassisType)\r\n| extend WiFiMAC = iff(\r\n    isnotempty(WiFiMacAddress) and strlen(WiFiMacAddress) == 12,\r\n    strcat(substring(WiFiMacAddress,0,2),\":\",substring(WiFiMacAddress,2,2),\":\",substring(WiFiMacAddress,4,2),\":\",substring(WiFiMacAddress,6,2),\":\",substring(WiFiMacAddress,8,2),\":\",substring(WiFiMacAddress,10,2)),\r\n    coalesce(WiFiMacAddress, \"—\"))\r\n| extend EthernetMAC = iff(\r\n    isnotempty(EthernetMacAddress) and strlen(EthernetMacAddress) == 12,\r\n    strcat(substring(EthernetMacAddress,0,2),\":\",substring(EthernetMacAddress,2,2),\":\",substring(EthernetMacAddress,4,2),\":\",substring(EthernetMacAddress,6,2),\":\",substring(EthernetMacAddress,8,2),\":\",substring(EthernetMacAddress,10,2)),\r\n    coalesce(EthernetMacAddress, \"—\"))\r\n| project\r\n    Office = coalesce(OfficeLocation, \"Not available\"),\r\n    City = coalesce(City, \"Not available\"),\r\n    Country = coalesce(Country, \"Not available\"),\r\n    [\"Form Factor\"] = FormFactor,\r\n    Ownership = coalesce(OwnerType, \"—\"),\r\n    [\"Serial Number\"] = coalesce(SerialNumber, \"—\"),\r\n    [\"Wi-Fi MAC\"] = WiFiMAC,\r\n    [\"Ethernet MAC\"] = EthernetMAC,\r\n    IMEI = coalesce(IMEI, \"—\")",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Location & Device Identity",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table"
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "deepdive-location-identity"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "> *Location fields (Office, City, Country) require **User.Read.All** permission on the app registration and will show \"Not available\" until enabled.*"
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "name": "deepdive-contact-note"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "---\n### Compliance"
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "name": "deepdive-section-compliance"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneComplianceStates_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId, PolicyId\r\n| where DeviceId == '{SelectedDeviceId}'\r\n| extend StatusLabel = case(\r\n    StatusRaw == 2, \"Compliant\",\r\n    StatusRaw == 3, \"In Grace Period\",\r\n    StatusRaw == 4, \"Non-Compliant\",\r\n    StatusRaw == 5, \"Error\",\r\n    StatusRaw == 6, \"Conflict\",\r\n    \"Other\")\r\n| summarize Policies = count() by StatusLabel",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "Policy Status Breakdown",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "piechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Compliant",
                    "color": "green"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Non-Compliant",
                    "color": "redBright"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Error",
                    "color": "orange"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "In Grace Period",
                    "color": "yellow"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Conflict",
                    "color": "purple"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Other",
                    "color": "gray"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "customWidth": "35",
            "name": "deepdive-compliance-pie"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneComplianceStates_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId, PolicyId\r\n| where DeviceId == '{SelectedDeviceId}'\r\n| extend StatusLabel = case(\r\n    StatusRaw == 2, 'Compliant',\r\n    StatusRaw == 3, 'InGracePeriod',\r\n    StatusRaw == 4, 'NonCompliant',\r\n    StatusRaw == 5, 'Error',\r\n    StatusRaw == 6, 'Conflict',\r\n    StatusRaw == 7, 'NotApplicable',\r\n    'Unknown')\r\n| project PolicyName, StatusLabel, FailedSettingCount, SettingCount, LastContact\r\n| order by case(\r\n    StatusLabel == \"NonCompliant\", 1, StatusLabel == \"Error\", 2, StatusLabel == \"Conflict\", 3,\r\n    StatusLabel == \"InGracePeriod\", 4, StatusLabel == \"Compliant\", 5, 6) asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Compliance Policy Details",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "StatusLabel",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Compliant",
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "Compliant"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "NonCompliant",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "NonCompliant"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Error",
                          "representation": "Sev0",
                          "text": "Error"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "InGracePeriod",
                          "representation": "warning",
                          "text": "InGracePeriod"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "unknown",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "FailedSettingCount",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": ">",
                          "thresholdValue": "0",
                          "representation": "warning",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "0"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "customWidth": "65",
            "name": "deepdive-compliance-table"
          },
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "---\n### Risk Assessment & Recommended Action"
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "name": "deepdive-section-risk"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let Device = IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where DeviceId == '{SelectedDeviceId}';\r\nlet UsersByUPN = IntuneUsers_CL | summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserPrincipalName;\r\nlet UsersByIdLookup = IntuneUsers_CL | summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by UserId;\r\nDevice\r\n| join kind=leftouter (UsersByUPN | project UserPrincipalName, AccountEnabled) on UserPrincipalName\r\n| join kind=leftouter (UsersByIdLookup | project LastLoggedOnUserId = UserId, LastLogonAccountEnabled = AccountEnabled) on LastLoggedOnUserId\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime)),\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled = coalesce(LastLogonAccountEnabled, AccountEnabled)\r\n| extend StaleSeverity = case(\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, \"Critical - 6+ months\", LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"High - 3-6 months\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 60, \"Medium - 2-3 months\", \"Low - 1-2 months\")\r\n| extend RecommendedAction = case(\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire - user disabled, device abandoned\",\r\n    isempty(UserPrincipalName) and isempty(LastLoggedOnUserId) and LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Retire - no user, long stale\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, \"Retire - 6+ months uncontacted\",\r\n    LastSyncDaysAgo > 90, \"Investigate - likely lost or decommissioned\",\r\n    BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Investigate - user disabled, device recent\",\r\n    \"Monitor - recently went stale\")\r\n| extend IsOrphaned = iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Yes\", iff(isnull(BestKnownAccountEnabled), \"Unknown\", \"No\"))\r\n| extend RiskFactors = strcat_array(array_concat(\r\n    iff(IsOrphaned == \"Yes\", dynamic([\"User account disabled\"]), dynamic([])),\r\n    iff(LastSyncDaysAgo > 180, dynamic([\"6+ months without sync\"]), dynamic([])),\r\n    iff(IsEncrypted != \"true\", dynamic([\"Device not encrypted\"]), dynamic([])),\r\n    iff(tolower(ComplianceState) == \"noncompliant\", dynamic([\"Non-compliant\"]), dynamic([]))), \", \")\r\n| project StaleSeverity, RecommendedAction, IsOrphaned,\r\n    UserAccount = iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == true, \"Active\", iff(BestKnownAccountEnabled == false, \"Disabled\", \"Unknown\")),\r\n    ComplianceState, IsEncrypted = case(IsEncrypted == \"true\", \"Yes\", IsEncrypted == \"false\", \"No\", \"Unknown\"),\r\n    RiskFactors",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Risk Assessment",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "StaleSeverity",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Critical",
                          "representation": "Sev0",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "High",
                          "representation": "Sev1",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Medium",
                          "representation": "Sev2",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "Sev3",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "RecommendedAction",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Retire",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "contains",
                          "thresholdValue": "Investigate",
                          "representation": "warning",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "pending",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "IsOrphaned",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "Yes",
                          "representation": "failed",
                          "text": "Yes"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "==",
                          "thresholdValue": "No",
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "No"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "unknown",
                          "text": "Unknown"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "conditionalVisibility": {
              "parameterName": "SelectedDeviceId",
              "comparison": "isNotEqualTo",
              "value": ""
            },
            "name": "deepdive-risk-assessment"
          }
        ]
      },
      "conditionalVisibility": {
        "parameterName": "Tab",
        "comparison": "isEqualTo",
        "value": "DeepDive"
      },
      "name": "deepdive-group"
    },
    {
      "type": 12,
      "content": {
        "version": "NotebookGroup/1.0",
        "groupType": "editable",
        "items": [
          {
            "type": 1,
            "content": {
              "json": "## Step 7: Trends & Patterns\n\nAnalyse how the stale device population has changed over time and identify hardware, OS, or organisational patterns that may explain why devices go stale."
            },
            "name": "trends-intro"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let StaleDays = toint({StaleDays});\r\nIntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| where TimeGenerated > ago(30d)\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend SnapshotDay = bin(TimeGenerated, 1d)\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, LastSyncDateTime) by DeviceId, SnapshotDay\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAtSnapshot = datetime_diff('day', SnapshotDay, todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAtSnapshot > StaleDays\r\n| summarize StaleCount = dcount(DeviceId) by SnapshotDay\r\n| order by SnapshotDay asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Stale Device Count Over Time (30 Days)",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "timechart"
            },
            "name": "trends-stale-count"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "let StaleDays = toint({StaleDays});\r\nIntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > StaleDays\r\n| extend WentStaleDate = datetime_add('day', StaleDays, todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where WentStaleDate > ago(90d)\r\n| extend StaleWeek = startofweek(WentStaleDate)\r\n| summarize NewStaleDevices = count() by StaleWeek\r\n| order by StaleWeek asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Newly Stale Devices Per Week (Last 90 Days)",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "xAxis": "StaleWeek",
                "yAxis": [
                  "NewStaleDevices"
                ],
                "showDataLabels": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "trends-newly-stale"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| summarize\r\n    StaleCount = count(),\r\n    AvgDaysStale = round(avg(LastSyncDaysAgo), 0),\r\n    MaxDaysStale = max(LastSyncDaysAgo),\r\n    Critical = countif(LastSyncDaysAgo > 180)\r\n    by Manufacturer, Model\r\n| order by StaleCount desc\r\n| take 20",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Stale Devices by Hardware Model",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "table",
              "gridSettings": {
                "formatters": [
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "StaleCount",
                    "formatter": 4,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "redBright"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "AvgDaysStale",
                    "formatter": 8,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "palette": "greenRed",
                      "min": 30,
                      "max": 365
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "columnMatch": "Critical",
                    "formatter": 18,
                    "formatOptions": {
                      "thresholdsOptions": "icons",
                      "thresholdsGrid": [
                        {
                          "operator": ">",
                          "thresholdValue": "0",
                          "representation": "Sev0",
                          "text": "{0}"
                        },
                        {
                          "operator": "Default",
                          "thresholdValue": null,
                          "representation": "success",
                          "text": "0"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "filter": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "trends-by-model"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| extend OSVersionLabel = coalesce(OSVersion, \"Unknown\")\r\n| summarize Devices = count() by OSVersionLabel\r\n| order by Devices desc\r\n| take 10",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Stale Devices by OS Version",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "xAxis": "OSVersionLabel",
                "yAxis": [
                  "Devices"
                ],
                "showDataLabels": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "trends-by-os"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| extend EnrollmentAge = datetime_diff('month', now(), todatetime(EnrolledDateTime))\r\n| extend AgeBucket = case(\r\n    EnrollmentAge <= 6, \"0-6 months\",\r\n    EnrollmentAge <= 12, \"6-12 months\",\r\n    EnrollmentAge <= 24, \"1-2 years\",\r\n    EnrollmentAge <= 36, \"2-3 years\",\r\n    EnrollmentAge <= 48, \"3-4 years\",\r\n    \"4+ years\")\r\n| summarize Devices = count() by AgeBucket\r\n| order by case(\r\n    AgeBucket == \"0-6 months\", 1,\r\n    AgeBucket == \"6-12 months\", 2,\r\n    AgeBucket == \"1-2 years\", 3,\r\n    AgeBucket == \"2-3 years\", 4,\r\n    AgeBucket == \"3-4 years\", 5,\r\n    6) asc",
              "size": 0,
              "title": "Stale Devices by Enrollment Age",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "barchart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "xAxis": "AgeBucket",
                "yAxis": [
                  "Devices"
                ],
                "showDataLabels": true
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "50",
            "name": "trends-by-enrollment-age"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| extend FormFactor = case(\r\n    ChassisType in (\"notebook\", \"laptop\"), \"Laptop\",\r\n    ChassisType in (\"desktop\", \"tower\", \"miniTower\", \"allInOne\"), \"Desktop\",\r\n    ChassisType == \"tablet\", \"Tablet\",\r\n    isempty(ChassisType) or ChassisType == \"unknown\", \"Unknown\",\r\n    tostring(ChassisType))\r\n| summarize Devices = count() by FormFactor\r\n| order by Devices desc",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "By Form Factor",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "piechart"
            },
            "customWidth": "33",
            "name": "trends-by-formfactor"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| extend ComplianceLabel = case(\r\n    tolower(ComplianceState) == \"compliant\", \"Compliant\",\r\n    tolower(ComplianceState) == \"noncompliant\", \"NonCompliant\",\r\n    tolower(ComplianceState) == \"ingraceperiod\", \"InGracePeriod\",\r\n    \"Unknown\")\r\n| summarize Devices = count() by ComplianceLabel\r\n| order by Devices desc",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "By Compliance State",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "piechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Compliant",
                    "color": "green"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "NonCompliant",
                    "color": "redBright"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "InGracePeriod",
                    "color": "yellow"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Unknown",
                    "color": "gray"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "33",
            "name": "trends-by-compliance"
          },
          {
            "type": 3,
            "content": {
              "version": "KqlItem/1.0",
              "query": "IntuneManagedDevices_CL\r\n| summarize arg_max(TimeGenerated, *) by DeviceId\r\n| where OperatingSystem startswith \"Windows\"\r\n| extend LastSyncDaysAgo = datetime_diff('day', now(), todatetime(LastSyncDateTime))\r\n| where LastSyncDaysAgo > toint({StaleDays})\r\n| extend EncryptionStatus = case(\r\n    IsEncrypted == \"true\", \"Encrypted\",\r\n    IsEncrypted == \"false\", \"Not Encrypted\",\r\n    \"Unknown\")\r\n| summarize Devices = count() by EncryptionStatus\r\n| order by Devices desc",
              "size": 1,
              "title": "By Encryption Status",
              "queryType": 0,
              "resourceType": "microsoft.operationalinsights/workspaces",
              "visualization": "piechart",
              "chartSettings": {
                "seriesLabelSettings": [
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Encrypted",
                    "color": "green"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Not Encrypted",
                    "color": "redBright"
                  },
                  {
                    "seriesName": "Unknown",
                    "color": "gray"
                  }
                ]
              }
            },
            "customWidth": "34",
            "name": "trends-by-encryption"
          }
        ]
